So for all you people who are supporting the Tzar, realize that this is what you are agreeing to, accepting in terms of international diplomacy, ignoring decency and honor.

Source: 
 https://www.abc.net.au/news/2022-03-30/ukraine-first-lady-olena-zelenska-refuses-to-flee-amid-war/100944068

