Front Page Edit: Thanks to everyone for the love! Your encouragement started this fire! I've got to figure out how I'm going to get this skin removed. I have a gofundme set up but I'm too afraid to share. I linked it in my Imgur bio. 

Goals update: Plans to move out are ever changing. I did settle my debt with my Aunt by selling my old car. I was naive to think that even with funds I could move quickly in this economic environment. My credit is slowly getting there and the apartment fund you folks raised is growing with my contributed savings. I'm going to get there. I think I need to get my June Alaska trip out of the way and give my credit time to get to a place where application rejection isn't going to happen. I already have too many looks at my credit getting the new car. I'm just going to continue to keep my head down and grind like I have been. Mistakes are expected to be made. It's how I react that matters. All feedback and advice is welcome! 

