 how it’s installed. The catheter goes directly into the main inlet vein of the heart. If it were just an arm IV, the risk is it could leak into the surrounding tissue which can damage it, since it’s such nasty stuff. 

I was very lucky that the kind of breast cancer I got is common and very well understood, and has incredibly effective drugs to fight it. Chemo and surgery was 100% effective, and I’m cancer free now! My doc even uses the word “cured,” not just in remission. 

I thought the device was nifty, so I wanted to share. Cheers, friends!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CodpxwI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tomicGoober]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Another thing that will be forgotten by tomorrow.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2374t1X</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C6GkdI4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U31nxqj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sauce: https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2022/mar/30/trump-used-white-house-phone-call-capitol-attack-jan-6-not-official-log</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2374t1X</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BluesFish]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Who will win?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KeFrID9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UU6e5qr.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KeFrID9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AgeingAss]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Oscar</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5z55iYY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KJlc7m1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5z55iYY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[dogdash4]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Universities are for grifters</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CryuZbv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6S9DWi1.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u6tRmjt.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7dzuyOO.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img